      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Official Glean docs to open alongside this diagram:\n\nIndexing API overview\nhttps://developers.glean.com/api/indexing-api/documents-overview\n\nSearch API overview\nhttps://developers.glean.com/api/client-api/search/overview\n\nChat API overview\nhttps://developers.glean.com/docs/client_api/chat_api/\n\nUse this with `memos/g-10-design-note.md` to map each runtime stage back to the implementation and the corresponding Glean API surface.",
      "baseline": 195,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Official Glean docs to open alongside this diagram:\n\nIndexing API overview\nhttps://developers.glean.com/api/indexing-api/documents-overview\n\nSearch API overview\nhttps://developers.glean.com/api/client-api/search/overview\n\nChat API overview\nhttps://developers.glean.com/docs/client_api/chat_api/\n\nUse this with `memos/g-10-design-note.md` to map each runtime stage back to the implementation and the corresponding Glean API surface.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "notesPanel",
