      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "How to read this against the code:\n\n1. Config drives both ingest and ask paths before any API calls are made.\n2. The fixture corpus is local-only and becomes Glean `DocumentDefinition` objects during ingest.\n3. `ingestFixtureCorpus()` uploads docs and tries `processAll()` for indexing completion.\n4. `retrieveSources()` calls Search first and normalizes the selected sources.\n5. `buildGroundedPrompt()` converts retrieval output into explicit context for Chat.\n6. `askQuestion()` calls Chat, extracts the assistant response, and appends citations.\n7. `src/cli.ts` and `src/mcp.ts` are thin wrappers over the shared workflow, which keeps the interview walkthrough and any live change concentrated in `src/workflow.ts`.",
      "baseline": 195,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How to read this against the code:\n\n1. Config drives both ingest and ask paths before any API calls are made.\n2. The fixture corpus is local-only and becomes Glean `DocumentDefinition` objects during ingest.\n3. `ingestFixtureCorpus()` uploads docs and tries `processAll()` for indexing completion.\n4. `retrieveSources()` calls Search first and normalizes the selected sources.\n5. `buildGroundedPrompt()` converts retrieval output into explicit context for Chat.\n6. `askQuestion()` calls Chat, extracts the assistant response, and appends citations.\n7. `src/cli.ts` and `src/mcp.ts` are thin wrappers over the shared workflow, which keeps the interview walkthrough and any live change concentrated in `src/workflow.ts`.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
  ],
  "appState": {
    "gridSize": null,
    "viewBackgroundColor": "#ffffff"
  },
